Type: Package
Package: mergenstudio
Title: A visual chatbot interface for AI-driven data analysis using the 'Mergen' package.
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jacqueline", "Jansen", , "jacqueline-98@hotmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
